Text:
Em Português:

O meu upload é muito limitado, por isso vai demorar algum tempo a ficar concluído.




English:

My upload is very limited, so will take some time to be completed.
Seed plz all of us stuck at 99.8 %, we can continue seeding once we reach 100%
Sorry people, but I was without internet for two months.
... and I'm not uploading it again.
